    <title>Viewing information copied from the structure panel</title>
    <shortdesc>CWRC-Writer provides the option of looking at what you have copied in the structure
        panel before you need to paste it in. This allows you to make sure you have selected exactly
        what you wanted to work with.</shortdesc>
